"NAME                                      \n"
"    testirqsave - test irq_save()         \n"
"SYNOPSIS                                  \n"
"    testirqsave [-h] [-i <irq_num>]       \n"
"DESCRIPTION                               \n"
"    1) sets handler on irq #irq_num       \n"
"    2) runs irq_save()                    \n"
"    3) calls irq #irq_num                 \n"
"    4) runs irq_restore()                 \n"
"    5) restores old handler on irq        \n"
"OPTION                                    \n"
"    -h -  to see this page                \n"
"    -i irq number  (default 10 (0xA))     \n"
"EXAMPLES                                  \n"
"    testirqsave -h                        \n"
"    testirqsave                           \n"
"    testirqsave -i 10                     \n"
"    testirqsave -i 0xA                    \n"
"AUTHORS                                   \n"
